Daimler - return on capital employed to rise . Daimler - Benz AG said on Thursday its return on capital employed would improve in 1997 to at least eight to nine percent , up from 5 . 2 percent at the end of 1996 . " If we assume second half proift would be the same as the first half , then our full - year return on capital employed would be eight to nine percent , " Daimler chief Juergen Schrempp told reporters at the company ' s half - year results conference . - - Bonn Newsroom , + 49 - 228 26097150 
